rows.label: qst202210_msg001
rows.name: Hey, it's the sparky girl!

rows.label: qst202210_msg002
rows.name: Mm?

rows.label: qst202210_msg003
rows.name: You gonna zap poor Izzi again?!

rows.label: qst202210_msg004
rows.name: Izzi is kid that Raiko zap before?

rows.label: qst202210_msg005
rows.name: Yeah. Poor little dizzy Izzi!

rows.label: qst202210_msg006
rows.name:
Uh, actually I'm here to apologize
to him. D'you know where he is?

rows.label: qst202210_msg007
rows.name:
Yeah, right, I bet you just wanna zap
him again!

rows.label: qst202210_msg008
rows.name:
It okay now! Raiko learn to control
zappy-zaps. No more buzzy-buzzy!

rows.label: qst202210_msg009
rows.name: ...What, really?

rows.label: qst202210_msg010
rows.name:
It true. Raiko try to help friends with
powers, not hurt.

rows.label: qst202210_msg019
rows.name:
Whole reason why Avaritia look
sparkly-sparkly because of Raiko!

rows.label: qst202210_msg020
rows.name:
Oh yeah, I heard about that.
I wish I could've seen it...

rows.label: qst202210_msg011
rows.name: Okay then, I'll trust you.

rows.label: qst202210_msg012
rows.name:
But hang on, Izzi's not around
right now.

rows.label: qst202210_msg013
rows.name: Can you tell me where he is then?

rows.label: qst202210_msg014
rows.name:
He said he was gonna collect some
rare bugs or something? I dunno.

rows.label: qst202210_msg015
rows.name:
He went off towards Koorell Pool,
so he's probably there?

rows.label: qst202210_msg016
rows.name:
Great, thanks! I'm gonna go look for
him now!

rows.label: qst202210_msg017
rows.name:
Fair enough. Just promise you two
are gonna make up, okay?

rows.label: qst202210_msg018
rows.name: Sure thing! Promise!
